latestPosts.caption: Hi! I appreciate you all that are here for laughs, shopping, jewelry tips and more! I’m Angel and I go by Midlifecrisisgirl. I started creating content because of my late sister who loved watching my TikToks during her cancer treatments, it made her laugh and she loved shopping! I’m born in the Philippines but am a true Californian! Say hi! Im kind, unless you’re gonna be mean, because unlike Michelle Obama, when they go low, I will go lower! 😌
My brand @worshipgaud is dropping it like it’s hot for the summer! Here is a sneak peek! Save 15% off this week! Enjoy! #jewelry

Wanna see what I bought?!! I’m such a good housewife! I was so productive and even cooked Joe a delicious fancy dinner! This is a day in a life but I am cosplaying as a Marin housewife. I kinda want to be one for realsies! #luxuryshopping #jewelryshopping #marin #bayarea #ditl #sahw

I went to Harwell Godfrey and ran into Nina! I met her before at the store and her jewelry style is immaculate! I may have influenced her to buy the #costco gold hoops! I loved her mix of Harwell, colorful stones, and vintage items! #jewelrystyling #jotd #jewelry #solidgold #costcofinds

this is an opinion piece about the slick bun brigade voicing opinions people didn’t like. This is my opinion that people who don’t take accountability is what is wrong in this online world. Stop blaming the consciences of your actions on others, this is all on you. If you didn’t start nothing, there would be nothing. I’m team millennialrx. Imagine this because you didn’t like pimple patches and didn’t let others just exist without inputting your opinion

Once I due some due diligence research on resources on how to help, I will share in my stories. This is a show of unnecessary force instill fear, but I know LA people are resilient and strong. California is great because of the immigrants we have, documented or not, we make California great.

Dainty jewelry, not me. It’s because I grew up on 90’s hip hop and their jewelry style was elite. Also, I’m a Cali girl (yes, natives say that), therefore love supporting Cali jewelry brands, we are so diverse! @icelinkofficial @auroro.world @a.tabz and of course my own @worshipgaud
